# Astro Agent — Cursor Rules (Auto-loaded Context)

## Project
Production-ready Astrologer AI Agent with RAG. Vedic astrology + palmistry PDFs → OCR → embeddings → vector search → LLM answer.

## Stack
- OCR: Tesseract + pytesseract + pdf2image
- Diagram interpretation: GPT-4o (one-time ingestion only)
- Embeddings: OpenAI text-embedding-3-small
- Vector DB: ChromaDB (local dev), Pinecone (production)
- Inference: GPT-4o-mini
- Backend: FastAPI
- Frontend: Streamlit (dev) → React (prod)
- Auth: Supabase
- Payments: Stripe

## Folder Structure
ingestion/     → pdf_processor.py, image_extractor.py, chunker.py, embedder.py
retrieval/     → query_engine.py, image_retriever.py
agent/         → astrologer.py, prompt_builder.py, session_manager.py
api/           → main.py, routes/, auth.py
frontend/      → app.py
data/pdfs/     → source PDFs
data/chroma_db/→ persistent vector store
data/extracted_images/ → diagram images
data/default_user/ → kundli_summary.txt, palm_description.txt (default user context)

## File Dependency Map
pdf_processor.py → outputs chunks + image_paths
chunker.py → consumes pdf_processor output
embedder.py → consumes chunker output → writes ChromaDB
query_engine.py → reads ChromaDB
astrologer.py → calls query_engine + prompt_builder

## Chunk Metadata Schema (locked — do not change)
{
  "chunk_id": "str",
  "text": "str",
  "topic": "str",
  "language": "eng|hin|mixed",
  "page_ref": "int",
  "image_path": "str|null",
  "book_name": "str",
  "page_type": "text|diagram"
}

## ChromaDB
- Collection name: "astro_chunks"
- Embedding dimension: 1536 (text-embedding-3-small)
- Persist directory: data/chroma_db/

## Coding Standards
- Python 3.11
- Production-quality, modular, scalable
- Brief inline comments
- Always use try/except with meaningful error messages
- No full file rewrites — surgical edits only
- Preserve all interfaces and metadata schemas
- User is senior analytics practitioner — no basics

