## Book Type Classification
Astrology books (planetary/house/dasa content):
- BPHS Vol 1, BPHS Vol 2, Phaladeepika, Saravali

Palmistry books (hand lines/mounts/zones content):
- Cheiro's Language of the Hand

## Topic Tags by Book (for chunk metadata)
- BPHS: houses, planets, dasas, yogas, predictions, remedies
- Phaladeepika: planetary strength, horoscope, timing
- Saravali: rasi, navamsa, planetary results
- Cheiro: palm lines, mounts, hand shape, fingers